title: Dušan Kolarević
content:
Dušan Kolarević (Serbian Cyrillic: Душан Коларевић; born 19 April 1987) is a former Serbian footballer who played as a midfielder.[1]

His father, also named Dušan, owns a company in Ćićevac, engaged in wood economy.[2]
